n, m = map(int, input().split())
    x = [0] * n
    s = [0] * n
    for i in range(n):
        s[i], x[i] = map(float, input().split())
    x.sort()
    s.sort()
    x.append(10**9)
    s.append(0)
    i = 0
    j = 0
    ans = 0
    while i < n:
        while j < n and s[j] * x[i] < m:
            j += 1
        if j == n:
            break
        ans += 1
        i = j
    print(ans)

N, Q = map(int, input().split())
    a = [0] * N
    for i in range(Q):
        q = input().split()
        if q[0] == '+':
            i, delta = int(q[1]), int(q[2])
            a[i] += delta
        else:
            i = int(q[1])
            s = 0
            while i > 0:
                s += a[i]
                i -= i & -i
            print(s)
